snippet.title: TS!UNDERSWAP - UnderEvent 2021 Presentation + Starlight Isles Teaser
snippet.description:
Read our latest GameJolt devlog! https://gamejolt.com/p/progress-report-march-2021-teasers-design-reveals-and-more-3w549iub

Here's our video segment from "UnderEvent," a presentation of UNDERTALE fan-games meant to celebrate the creative talents of this community. We start by going over our project's history, give some insight on what we've learned, and finish off with a preview of the next area: Starlight Isles!

Check out the full UnderEvent 2021 video here! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aOadit6diGE

Voiced by Beethovenus
Video created by @Ethosein
TS!UNDERSWAP by Team Switched
UNDERTALE by Toby Fox (We are not affiliated!)

[0:00] Introduction
[1:04] Our History
[4:27] Starlight Isles Teaser

--

TS!UNDERSWAP is an unofficial fan-game of Toby Fox's UNDERTALE, made by Team Switched (TS).
It is a re-imagining based on the premise of swapping character roles, and adding original content, to create new scenarios.

By doing so, we aim to provide a brand new experience for fans of UNDERTALE, while staying true to its aesthetic and characters.

Like the project? Make sure to follow our progress!
Website - https://teamswitched.gamejolt.io/
GameJolt - https://gamejolt.com/games/tsunderswap/160094
Discord - https://discord.gg/aYNKEBzwNf
Tumblr - https://tsunderswapofficial.tumblr.com/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/tswitched
Official Wiki - https://tsunderswapofficial.wikia.com/wiki/TS!Underswap_Wiki
